00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:06,914
害怕并不是过错
'Cause there's nothin' wrong with bein' afraid.

396
00:32:06,956 --> 00:32:10,289
害怕是对陌生环境的敏感反应
Fear's a sensible response to an unfamiliar situation.

397
00:32:10,326 --> 00:32:15,123
陌生的危险环境 有一条喷火的龙
Unfamiliar dangerous situation, I might add. With a dragon 

398
00:32:12,724 --> 00:32:15,123
that breathes fire and eats knights and breathes fire,

399
00:32:15,131 --> 00:32:18,658
害怕并不意味着你是胆小鬼
it sure doesn't mean you're a coward if you're a little scared.

400
00:32:18,701 --> 00:32:21,602
我确信史莱克不是胆小鬼
I sure as heck ain't no coward. I know that. [ Gasps ]

401
00:32:23,072 --> 00:32:26,166
驴，两件事，好吗？
Donkey, two things, okay?

402
00:32:26,843 --> 00:32:31,614
闭嘴，去看看能不能找到楼梯
Shut... up. Now go over there and see if you can find any stairs.

403
