459
00:37:49,632 --> 00:37:52,931
让我们回头一步一步地来
Okay, okay. Let's just back up a little and take this one step at a time.

460
00:37:52,968 --> 00:37:57,166
我们真的应该 先做个朋友或者笔友
We really should get to know each other first as friends or pen pals.

461
00:37:57,206 --> 00:38:01,438
我经常在路上旅行 但我喜欢接收明信片...
I'm on the road a lot, but I just love receiving cards--

462
00:38:01,477 --> 00:38:03,968
我确实想留下，但...
I'd really love to stay, but--

463
00:38:04,013 --> 00:38:06,641
别这样！这是我私人的尾巴
Don't do that! That's my tail! That's my personal tail.

464
00:38:06,682 --> 00:38:10,118
你要去掉？你要用它做什么？
You're gonna tear it off. I don't give permission-- What are you gonna do with that?

465
00:38:10,186 --> 00:38:14,020
现在！不行，不！
Hey, now. No way. No! No!

466
00:38:14,090 --> 00:38:16,854
不！不！不！
No, no! No. No, no, no! No! Oh!

467
00:38:43,619 --> 00:38:45,587
- 嗨，公主！ - 它会说话！
- Hi, Princess! - It talks!

468
00:38:45,654 --> 00:38:48,987
对，让他闭嘴得用窍门
Yeah, it's getting him to shut up that's the trick.

469
00:39:24,894 --> 00:39:26,953
好，你们俩，朝出口前进！
Okay, you two, head for the exit!

470
00:39:28,697 --> 00:39:31,359
我来对付龙
I'll take care of the dragon.

471
00:39:37,273 --> 00:39:42,677
跑
Run!

472
00:40:24,253 --> 00:40:31,794
你成功了！你救了我！ 真令人惊叹，你...
- [ Dragon Growling In The Distance ] - You did it! You rescued me! You're amazing. You're--

473
00:40:31,794 --> 00:40:33,921
你太伟大了，你是...
You're wonderful. You're...

474
00:40:35,764 --> 00:40:38,062
我得承认，有点儿怪
a little unorthodox I'll admit.

475
00:40:38,100 --> 00:40:42,730
但你的行为伟大，心底纯洁
But thy deed is great, and thine heart is pure.

476
00:40:43,372 --> 00:40:45,363
我将永远感激你
- I am eternally in your debt. - [ Clears Throat ]

477
00:40:47,042 --> 00:40:51,308
没有高贵的马 哪里有勇敢的骑士？
And where would a brave knight be without his noble steed?

478
00:40:51,413 --> 00:40:56,180
我希望你听到了这些话 她说我是高贵的马！
I hope you heard that. She called me a noble steed. She think I'm a steed.

479
00:40:56,252 --> 00:41:02,016
战斗打赢了 可以摘掉头盔了，好骑士先生
[ Fiona Laughs ] The battle is won. You may remove your helmet, good Sir Knight.

480
00:41:02,091 --> 00:41:06,962
- 为什么不？ - 我的头发被压扁了
- Uh, no. - Why not? I have helmet hair.

481
00:41:06,962 --> 00:41:10,227
求你，我想看看救我人的脸
Please. I would'st look upon the face of my rescuer.

482
00:41:10,266 --> 00:41:13,035
- 不，不，你不想... 
No, no, you wouldn't-- 'st.

483
00:41:13,035 --> 00:41:21,777
- 可你怎么吻我？ - 这不在工作的要求里 - 也许是个奖赏
But how will you kiss me? What? That wasn't in the job description. Maybe it's a perk.

484
00:41:21,777 --> 00:41:26,214
不，是命运 你一定要知道是怎么回事
No, it's destiny. Oh, you must know how it goes.

485
00:41:26,248 --> 00:41:30,082
一个被关在塔楼里 由龙看守的公主
A princess locked in a tower and beset by a dragon...

486
00:41:30,119 --> 00:41:33,111
被一个勇敢的骑士搭救了
is rescued by a brave knight,

487
00:41:33,155 --> 00:41:37,182
然后他们分享了 真正爱人的第一个吻
and then they share true love's first kiss.

488
00:41:37,293 --> 00:41:41,964
和史莱克？你想...等等 你以为他是你真正的爱人？
Hmm? With Shrek? You think-- Wait. Wait. You think that Shrek is your true love?

489
00:41:41,964 --> 00:41:44,057
是啊！
Well, yes.

490
00:41:48,003 --> 00:41:52,573
- 史莱克是你真正的爱人！ - 这有什么好笑的？
You think Shrek is your true love! What is so funny?

491
00:41:52,608 --> 00:41:59,338
- 我不是你喜欢的那种 - 不，你是，你救了我
Let's just say I'm not your type, okay? Of course, you are. You're my rescuer.

492
00:42:00,082 --> 00:42:04,181
- 现在，摘掉你的头盔 - 这不是个好主意
Now-- Now remove your helmet. Look. I really don't think this is a good idea.

493
00:42:04,186 --> 00:42:06,245
- 就把头盔摘掉 - 不
-Just take off the helmet. - I'm not going to.

494
00:42:06,288 --> 00:42:09,625
-摘掉，现在！ - 好！
- Take it off. - No! - Now! - Okay!

495
00:42:09,625 --> 00:42:13,891
别发火，听从你的命令，阁下
Easy. As you command, Your Highness.

496
00:42:24,306 --> 00:42:27,742
你...你是个妖怪
You-- You're a--an ogre.

497
00:42:27,810 --> 00:42:34,305
- 你以为我像王子一样漂亮？ - 嗯，对，是这样的
Oh, you were expecting Prince Charming. Well, yes, actually.

498
00:42:36,652 --> 00:42:41,887
不，都搞错了 你不应该是个妖怪
Oh, no. This is all wrong. You're not supposed to be an ogre.

499
00:42:42,891 --> 00:42:47,191
公主，我是被法阔德勋爵 派来救你的
[ Sighs ] Princess, I was sent to rescue you by Lord Farquaad, okay?

500
00:42:47,229 --> 00:42:51,200
- 是他想跟你结婚 - 那他为什么不来救我？
He's the one who wants to marry you. Then why didn't he come rescue me?

501
00:42:51,200 --> 00:42:55,603
好问题，到那里后你去问他
Good question. You should ask him that when we get there.

502
00:42:55,704 --> 00:42:58,673
但我该被真正的爱人搭救
But I have to be rescued by my true love,

503
00:42:58,707 --> 00:43:01,574
而不是被妖怪和他的宠物搭救
not by some ogre and his-- his pet.

504
00:43:01,610 --> 00:43:06,440
- 再也不是高贵的马了 - 你使我的工作更麻烦了
So much for noble steed. You're not making my job any easier.

505
00:43:06,448 --> 00:43:09,884
对不起 你的工作不是我的问题
I'm sorry, but your job is not my problem.

506
00:43:09,918 --> 00:43:15,151
你去告诉法阔德 如果他想体面地救我
You can tell Lord Farquaad that if he wants to rescue me properly,

507
00:43:15,190 --> 00:43:17,658
我就在这里等他
I'll be waiting for him right here.

508
00:43:17,693 --> 00:43:22,721
我不是个送信的 我是个送货的
Hey! I'm no one's messenger boy, all right? I'm a delivery boy.

509
00:43:22,798 --> 00:43:27,169
- 你不敢，把我放下！ - 你来吗，驴？
You wouldn't dare. - Put me down! - Ya comin', Donkey?

510
00:43:27,169 --> 00:43:29,194
我就在你后面
I'm right behind ya.

511
00:43:29,271 --> 00:43:32,832
放下我，不然你将自食其果！
Put me down, or you will suffer the consequences!

512
00:43:32,875 --> 00:43:35,400
这太没有尊严了！放下我！
This is not dignified! Put me down! [ Screams ]

513
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,439
现在又有个问题
Okay, so here's another question.

514
00:43:40,516 --> 00:43:43,542
有个女人她喜欢你 但你不喜欢她
Say there's a woman that digs you, right, but you don't really like her that way.

515
00:43:43,585 --> 00:43:48,646
怎么才能容易地摆脱她 而不被她烧伤吃掉呢？
How do you let her down real easy so her feelings aren't hurt, but you don't get burned to a crisp and eaten?

516
00:43:48,657 --> 00:43:51,285
就告诉她 她不是你真正爱的人
You just tell her she's not your true love.

517
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:54,227
当发现了真爱时 每个人都明白会...
Everyone knowest what happens when you find your--

518
00:43:56,932 --> 00:43:59,298
越早赶到达罗克越好
The sooner we get to DuLoc the better.

519
00:43:59,334 --> 00:44:02,269
你会喜欢那里的 那里很美丽！
You're gonna love it there, Princess. It's beautiful!

520
00:44:02,304 --> 00:44:06,104
我的未婚夫法阔德怎么样？ 他长得什么样？
And what of my groom-to-be? Lord Farquaad? What's he like?

521
00:44:06,175 --> 00:44:08,370
我这样来说吧，公主
Let me put it this way, Princess.

522
00:44:08,410 --> 00:44:13,177
像法阔德那样矮的人很少
Men of Farquaad's stature are in short supply.

523
00:44:14,450 --> 00:44:18,147
我不知道，有人很少瞧见他
I don't know. There are those who think little of him.

524
00:44:20,656 --> 00:44:23,557
停下，你俩都停下
Stop it. Stop it, both of you.

525
00:44:23,592 --> 00:44:28,689
你们是在嫉妒 你们没法跟法阔德勋爵比
You're just jealous you can never measure up to a great ruler like Lord Farquaad.

526
00:44:28,731 --> 00:44:31,393
对，也许你说得对，公主
Yeah, well, maybe you're right, Princess.

527
00:44:31,433 --> 00:44:35,062
但明天见到他时 你最好亲自量量他
But I'll let you do the ''measuring'' when you see him tomorrow.

528
00:44:35,104 --> 00:44:38,835
明天？要等那么久啊？
Tomorrow? It'll take that long?

529
00:44:39,374 --> 00:44:44,141
- 我们停下露营吧？ - 不，那会更久
- Shouldn't we stop to make camp? - No, that'll take longer.

530
00:44:44,179 --> 00:44:48,616
- 我们接着走吧 - 但树林林里可能有强盗
- We can keep going. - But there's robbers in the woods.

531
00:44:48,650 --> 00:44:52,086
停下！露营现在听起来不错！
Whoa! Time out, Shrek! Camping's starting to sound good.

532
00:44:52,121 --> 00:44:56,251
我比这个森林里 任何的东西都更可怕
Hey, come on. I'm scarier than anything we're going to see in this forest.

533
00:44:56,291 --> 00:44:58,725
我要找个地方露营！
I need to find somewhere to camp now!

534
00:45:05,467 --> 00:45:09,631
- 过来 - 可以找个更好的地方
- Hey! Over here. - Shrek, we can do better than that.

535
00:45:09,671 --> 00:45:12,299
这不适合公主
I don't think this is fit for a princess.

536
00:45:12,341 --> 00:45:15,242
很完美 再来几下家庭的润色就行了
No, no, it's perfect. It just needs a few homey touches.

537
00:45:15,277 --> 00:45:18,212
家庭的润色？像什么？
- Homey touches? Like what? - [ Crashing ]

538
00:45:20,249 --> 00:45:24,379
一扇门？先生，祝你们晚安
A door? Well, gentlemen, I bid thee good night.

539
00:45:24,419 --> 00:45:29,454
- 睡前我给你讲个故事吧？ - 我说过晚安！
You want me to read you a bedtime story? I will. I said good night!

540
00:45:32,027 --> 00:45:34,723
史莱克，你在干什么？
Shrek, what are you doing?

541
00:45:34,797 --> 00:45:39,693
我只...你知道...别担心 我只是开玩笑
[ Laughs ] I just-- You know-- Oh, come on. I was just kidding.

542
00:45:43,005 --> 00:45:48,206
那个，那是斯洛白克
[ Fire Crackling ] And, uh, that one, that's Throwback,

543
00:45:48,243 --> 00:45:52,043
惟一吐过三块麦地的妖怪
the only ogre to ever spit over three wheat fields.

544
00:45:52,114 --> 00:45:54,275
对，好
Right. Yeah.

545
00:45:55,651 --> 00:45:58,211
你能看星相说出我的未来吗？
Hey, can you tell my future from these stars?

546
00:45:58,253 --> 00:46:01,916
星相不能告诉我们未来 他们告诉我们故事
The stars don't tell the future, Donkey. They tell stories.

547
00:46:01,957 --> 00:46:05,393
瞧，布拉纳特臭气
Look, there's Bloodnut, the Flatulent.

548
00:46:05,460 --> 00:46:09,328
- 你可以猜出它为什么出名 - 你在编造
- You can guess what he's famous for. - I know you're making this up.

549
00:46:09,364 --> 00:46:15,360
不，瞧，它在那里 猎人都臭跑了
No, look. There he is, and there's the group of hunters running away from his stench.

550
00:46:15,404 --> 00:46:18,931
它们只是群小星星
That ain't nothin' but a bunch of little dots.

551
00:46:19,007 --> 00:46:22,033
有时候事情 并不像表面上那么简单
Sometimes things are more than they appear.

552
00:46:24,313 --> 00:46:26,338
算了吧
Forget it.

553
00:46:29,484 --> 00:46:32,885
回到我们的沼泽地后 我们做什么？
Hey, Shrek, what we gonna do when we get our swamp anyway?

554
00:46:32,921 --> 00:46:36,983
- 我们的沼泽地？ - 我们救了公主
Our swamp? You know, when we're through rescuing the princess.

555
00:46:36,992 --> 00:46:41,793
我们？驴，没有“我们” 没有“我们的”
We? Donkey, there's no ''we.'' There's no ''our.''

556
00:46:41,830 --> 00:46:43,855
那是我的沼泽地
There's just me and my swamp.

557
00:46:43,899 --> 00:46:48,461
我要做的第一件事 就是建个十英尺高的围墙
The first thing I'm gonna do is build a ten-foot wall around my land.

558
00:46:48,570 --> 00:46:54,472
你伤害了我 你刚才深深地伤害了我
You cut me deep, Shrek. You cut me real deep just now.

559
00:46:54,509 --> 00:46:59,706
我想围墙只是为了堵人
You know what I think? I think this whole wall thing is just a way to keep somebody out.

560
00:46:59,715 --> 00:47:02,240
不，你这么想？
- No, do ya think? 

561
00:47:02,851 --> 00:47:06,020
- 你在隐瞒什么？ - 没什么
- Are you hidin' something?Never mind, Donkey.

562
00:47:06,054 --> 00:47:09,490
这是另一个洋葱的问题 对不对？
Oh, this is another one of those onion things, isn't it?

563
00:47:09,524 --> 00:47:13,153
不，这是个“别谈了”的问题
No, this is one of those drop-it and leave-it-alone things.

564
00:47:13,228 --> 00:47:16,994
- 你为什么不想谈呢？ - 你为什么想谈？
- Why don't you want to talk about it? - Why do you want to?

565
00:47:17,032 --> 00:47:18,897
- 你为什么要抑制自己？ - 我没有
- Why are you blocking? - I'm not blocking.

566
00:47:18,934 --> 00:47:21,232
- 你在抑制 - 我在警告你
- Oh, yes, you are. - Donkey, I'm warning you.

567
00:47:21,270 --> 00:47:24,762
- 你想堵住谁？ - 每个人！行了吧？
- Who you trying to keep out? - Everyone! Okay?

568
00:47:26,108 --> 00:47:31,909
- 现在我们有所进展了 - 看在圣彼得的面上！
Oh, now we're gettin' somewhere. Oh! For the love of Pete!

569
00:47:31,947 --> 00:47:36,748
- 你对世界有什么不满？ - 不是我有不满
What's your problem? What you got against the whole world? I'm not the one with the problem, okay?

570
00:47:36,818 --> 00:47:39,753
世界看起来对我不满
It's the world that seems to have a problem with me.

571
00:47:39,788 --> 00:47:47,558
人们看我一眼说 “救命！一个大丑妖怪！”
People take one look at me and go, ''Aah! Help! Run! A big, stupid, ugly ogre!''

572
00:47:48,297 --> 00:47:53,834
他们不了解我就下了结论 这就是为什么我最好一个人
[ Sighs ] They judge me before they even know me. That's why I'm better off alone.

573
00:48:02,611 --> 00:48:04,046
你知道吗？我们见面时
You know what?

574
00:48:04,046 --> 00:48:09,846
我没有认为你是个大丑妖怪
When we met, I didn't think you was just a big, stupid, ugly ogre.

575
00:48:09,885 --> 00:48:16,224
- 对，我知道 - 那么，天上有驴吗？
Yeah, I know. So, uh, are there any donkeys up there?

576
00:48:16,224 --> 00:48:22,059
嗯，有个多嘴的驴 是个讨厌的小家伙
Well, there's, um, Gabby, the Small and Annoying.

577
00:48:22,064 --> 00:48:27,058
我看到了，一个闪亮的大家伙 就在那里，那边那个？
Okay, I see it now. The big shiny one, right there. That one there?

578
00:48:27,102 --> 00:48:29,593
- 那是月亮 - 啊，对
- That's the moon. - Oh, okay.

579
00:48:52,494 --> 00:48:54,894
再给我看看
[ Farquaad ] Again. Show me again.

580
00:48:58,667 --> 00:49:02,660
镜子，镜子，让我再看看她 让我再看看公主
Mirror, mirror, show her to me. Show me the princess.

581
00:49:06,875 --> 00:49:11,676
十全十美
Ah. Perfect. [ Inhales ]

582
00:50:15,577 --> 00:50:20,549
对，你知道我喜欢这样 宝贝儿，我说过就喜欢这样
Mmm,yeah,you know I like it like that. - Come on, baby. I said I like it. - Donkey, wake up.

583
00:50:20,549 --> 00:50:26,221
- 驴，醒醒 - 什么？
- Huh? What? - Wake up. - What? - Good morning.

584
00:50:26,221 --> 00:50:30,157
史莱克，你喜欢吃啥样的蛋？
How do you like your eggs?

585
00:50:30,225 --> 00:50:34,252
- 早安，公主！ - 这是怎么回事？
- Good morning, Princess! - What's all this about?

586
00:50:34,296 --> 00:50:38,323
我们昨天开始得不好
We kind of got off to a bad start yesterday.

587
00:50:38,366 --> 00:50:45,031
我想弥补一下儿 我是说，毕竟你救了我
I wanted to make it up to you. After all, you did rescue me.

588
00:50:45,974 --> 00:50:48,067
谢谢
- Uh, thanks. - [ Sniffs ]

589
00:50:48,110 --> 00:50:52,012
吃吧，今天会很忙
Well, eat up. We've got a big day ahead of us.

590
00:50:56,451 --> 00:51:03,125
什么？这是赞美 我总是说出气比进气好
- [ Belches ] - Shrek! What? It's a compliment. Better out than in, I always say. [ Laughs ]

591
00:51:03,125 --> 00:51:06,686
在公主面前不能这样
- Well, it's no way to behave in front of a princess. - [ Belches ]

592
00:51:06,728 --> 00:51:09,959
- 谢谢 - 她和你一样粗野
- Thanks. - She's as nasty as you are.

593
00:51:10,899 --> 00:51:14,835
你知道，你不像我想像的那样
[ Laughs ] You know, you're not exactly what I expected.

594
00:51:14,870 --> 00:51:19,204
也许在不了解之前 不该下结论
Maybe you shouldn't judge people before you get to know them.

595
00:51:22,777 --> 00:51:25,143
解放了！
[ Man ] La liberte! Hey!

596
00:51:25,213 --> 00:51:27,147
公主
Princess!

597
00:51:27,449 --> 00:51:29,849
你要干什么？
- [ Laughs ] - What are you doing?

598
00:51:29,885 --> 00:51:32,877
别动，我亲爱的 因为我是你的救星！
Be still, mon cherie, for I am your savior!

599
00:51:32,921 --> 00:51:40,061
我从这个绿...兽掌中 救出了你
And I am rescuing you from this green-- [ Kissing Sounds ] - beast. - Hey!

600
00:51:40,061 --> 00:51:42,495
这是我的公主！去找你的吧！
That's my princess! Go find your own!

601
00:51:42,531 --> 00:51:47,594
巨兽！ 你没看见我正忙着吗？
Please, monster! Can't you see I'm a little busy here?

602
00:51:47,669 --> 00:51:51,264
瞧，伙计，我不知道你是谁...
Look, pal, I don't know who you think you are!

603
00:51:51,306 --> 00:51:56,077
当然！多么粗野 我来介绍一下儿我自己
Oh! Of course! Oh, how rude. Please let me introduce myself.

604
00:51:56,077 --> 00:51:58,045
伙计们！
